name: ForceModeEnum
description: Enumeration of force modes for applying forces to rigidbodies and characters.

staticFields.label: Force
staticFields.description: Force mode: applies force continuously over time.

staticFields.label: Acceleration
staticFields.description: Acceleration mode: applies force as acceleration, ignoring mass.

staticFields.label: Impulse
staticFields.description: Impulse mode: applies force instantly as an impulse.

staticFields.label: VelocityChange
staticFields.description: VelocityChange mode: applies force as a direct velocity change, ignoring mass.
